# .claude/settings.local
# Repository-specific Claude Code settings for stm32c071 project
# Actions whitelisted by user permission throughout development

## Whitelisted Tools & Commands
# These actions have been approved and do not require re-confirmation

# File Creation & Writing
- write: .claude/** (bugs, plans, research, tracking files)
- write: create new files for bug tracking and documentation

# Build & Flash Commands
- bash: python build.py
- bash: python build.py --clean
- bash: python flash.py
- bash: python run.py
- bash: python monitor_com4.py

# File Operations
- read: Core/Src/**
- read: Core/Inc/**
- read: CMakeLists.txt
- read: CMakePresets.json
- read: build.py
- read: flash.py
- read: run.py
- read: requirements.md
- read: docs/**

# Search & Analysis
- grep: search C code for patterns
- glob: find C/H files by pattern

# Git Operations
- bash: git status
- bash: git log
- bash: git diff

## Notes
# Add new whitelisted actions as they are approved during development
# Format: tool_name: description or command pattern
